comments: Poole (WAS) is moving alongside Osman's (SAS) path and cleanly dislodges the ball as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Vassell (SAS) is moving alongside Kuzma's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Coulibaly (WAS) steps slightly forward towards Vassell's (SAS) path, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Kuzma (WAS) is firming up over his right leg in Jones' (SAS) path, and he absorbs the contact during the pick.
Vassell (SAS) turns into Gafford (WAS) and delivers contact during the screen.
Kuzma (WAS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Spurs.
Kuzma (WAS) is moving alongside Johnson's (SAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as Johnson loses control of the ball on his own during his spin move.
Johnson (SAS) loses control of the ball on his own, and does not resumes his dribble upon regaining control of the ball.
Vassell (SAS) is the first player to touch the ball in the backcourt.
Vassell (SAS) immediately slides his hand off of Kuzma's (WAS) side and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Kuzma (WAS) clamps and holds Wembanyama's (SAS) shoulder and the contact affects Wembanyama's ability to pursue the rebound.
Jones (SAS) brushes Gafford's (WAS) arm and marginal arm contact occurs during his layup attempt.
Wembanyama (SAS) and Gafford's (WAS) come together off-ball and incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs as they disengage.
Gafford (WAS) brings his hand forward and makes contact with Wembanyama's (SAS) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) briefly grasps and immediately releases Johnson's (SAS) jersey, and the contact as they pursue the rebound is marginal.
Kuzma (WAS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Spurs.
